		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" /><div class="quotetitle"><b>Quote:</b></div><div class="quotecontent">Is there a way for a program to detect a poorly designed clone [...]</div>
<br />Sure, just package all my validation tests in first. :)
<br />
<br />The way to detect a clone is the same as with Nesticle: invoke some behavior that it differs for. We'd need to do research on each clone to find the problems, then hopefully narrow them down to a common subset.

		

